#: ../../docs/training_manual/complete_analysis/assignment.rst:2
msgid "Assignment"
msgstr "Opdracht"

#: ../../docs/training_manual/complete_analysis/assignment.rst:4
msgid ""
"Using the print layout, make a new map representing the results of your "
"analysis. Include these layers:"
msgstr ""
"Maak, met behulp van de afdruklay-out, een nieuwe kaart die de resultaten "
"van uw analyse weergeeft. Neem deze lagen er in op:"

#: ../../docs/training_manual/complete_analysis/assignment.rst:7
msgid "``places`` (with labels),"
msgstr "``places`` (met labels),"

#: ../../docs/training_manual/complete_analysis/assignment.rst:8
msgid "``hillshade``,"
msgstr "``Schaduw voor heuvels``,"

#: ../../docs/training_manual/complete_analysis/assignment.rst:9
msgid "``solution`` (or ``new_solution``),"
msgstr "``solution`` (of ``new_solution``),"

#: ../../docs/training_manual/complete_analysis/assignment.rst:10
msgid "``roads`` and"
msgstr "``roads`` en"

#: ../../docs/training_manual/complete_analysis/assignment.rst:11
msgid "either ``aerial_photos`` or ``DEM``."
msgstr "ofwel ``lucht_foto's`` of ``DEM``."

#: ../../docs/training_manual/complete_analysis/assignment.rst:13
msgid ""
"Write a short explanatory text to accompany it. Include in this text the "
"criteria that were used in considering a house for purchase and subsequent "
"development, as well as explaining your recommendations for which buildings "
"are suitable."
msgstr ""
"Schrijf een korte verklarende tekst om erbij te voegen. Neem in die tekst de"
" criteria op die werden gebruikt in de overweging om een huis aan te kopen "
"en aanvullend te ontwikkelen, als ook een verklaring voor uw aanbeveling "
"over welke gebouwen geschikt zijn."
